msgid "SECTION 1"
msgstr ""

msgid "Information We Collect"
msgstr "Impormasyong Kinokolekta Namin"

msgid "a. Account Information (if you sign in)"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"If you create an account, we collect your <strong class=\"text-"
"slate-700\">email address</strong> and <strong class=\"text-"
"slate-700\">name</strong>. This data is sent to our server (<strong "
"class=\"text-slate-700\">wird.me</strong>) to manage your session. "
"Authentication tokens are stored encrypted on your device only."
msgstr ""

msgid "b. Firebase Device Token (FCM)"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"We use Firebase Cloud Messaging (by Google) to deliver push notifications. "
"An anonymous device token is generated by Firebase and sent to our server. "
"This token does not personally identify you, is used only to send "
"notifications, and is refreshed automatically by the OS."
msgstr ""

msgid "c. Contact Messages"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"If you use the Contact Us feature, we receive the message you write and the "
"email you provide."
msgstr ""

msgid "SECTION 2"
msgstr ""

msgid "Data Stored Only on Your Device"
msgstr "Data na Nakaimbak Lamang sa Iyong Device"

msgid ""
"The following data is stored locally and <strong class=\"text-"
"slate-700\">never transmitted</strong>:"
msgstr ""

msgid "Reading progress, Khatmah plan, and Wird position"
msgstr ""

msgid "Azkar completion progress"
msgstr ""

msgid "Notification schedule and preferences"
msgstr ""

msgid "Selected reciter and Mushaf style"
msgstr ""

msgid "Accessibility and display settings"
msgstr ""

msgid "Downloaded Mushaf images and audio files"
msgstr ""

msgid "The Quran database"
msgstr ""

msgid "SECTION 3"
msgstr ""

msgid "Microphone Access"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"If you enable the <strong class=\"text-slate-700\">Voice Commands</strong> "
"accessibility feature, the app uses your device microphone to recognise "
"spoken Arabic navigation commands."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"All voice processing happens locally on your device. No audio is sent to our "
"servers or any third party."
msgstr ""

msgid "SECTION 4"
msgstr ""

msgid "Third-Party Services"
msgstr "Mga Serbisyo ng Third-Party"

msgid "Service"
msgstr ""

msgid "Provider"
msgstr ""

msgid "Purpose"
msgstr ""

msgid "Push notifications"
msgstr ""

msgid "App initialisation"
msgstr ""

